= IMG_SavePNG =

Save a SDL_Surface into a PNG image file.

== Syntax ==

<syntaxhighlight lang='c'>
int IMG_SavePNG(SDL_Surface *surface, const char *file);
</syntaxhighlight>

== Function Parameters ==

{|
|'''surface'''
|SDL surface to save
|-
|'''file'''
|file name
|}

== Return Value ==

Returns 0 if successful, -1 on error

